               <p>I am constable; I apprehended the prisoner, and searched him, but found nothing at all upon him; I found nothing at his house; I found a duplicate in Bates's pocket which led me to the house of a woman of the name of 
               <persName id="t17960406-83-person906">
                  Martha
                   Davis
               <interp inst="t17960406-83-person906" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
